":"2020-07-07T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"pr公司 玩分化 小心 <br />\n請無視分化post   <br />\n中共可能取消九月的選舉，<br />\n請用初選表達民意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"你都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜鳩都pr 公司<br />\n問題係佢借d e 唔同人講今次係實名投票呀<br />\n不如我話你係泛民pr 啦好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a69befac44d10598c97cb9564e94ae63c82deda","tid":2098141,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"defd80a745a101b3376da249a9090caf11c48423","tid":2098141,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"只會投黃碧雲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n一齊衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858a21dbc30aac3806930bb133ef4c9df2c01f30","tid":2098141,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"149b83d8af4134ee70ef1367295dea38c60bb434","tid":2098141,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:26:55.000Z","msg":"重點唔係果個已經廢左既立法會<br />\n係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>選左出黎既人同埋佢背後所代表既民意</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以初選時既民意back up, 就算到時香港正式鎖港封網，只要有初選獲勝既既議員成功走出國際<br />\n佢地可以幫香港人做好多事<br />\n<br />\n因為係國際眼中<br />\n佢地就係香港Pro-Democracy既代表<br />\n之後無論佢地做乜野都會增大我地既牙力<br />\n<br />\n例如成立外國流亡議會，代香港人發聲，或者做lobbying<br />\n所以初選之後出黎既人<br />\n即使比人DQ，即使立法會收皮<br />\n我地都可以壯大國際戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:16:10.000Z","msg":"１。長毛<br />\n主持問：你點睇新一代抗爭者 以攬炒為前提進入議會呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrL0VYi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrL0VYi.gif&h=068d8f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">片:</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/e00bwo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fe00bwo&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=6139e151\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/e00bwo</a><br />\n<br />\n２。涂謹申<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qCjmKYz2eU4?t=4027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqCjmKYz2eU4%3Ft%3D4027&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=f6e418b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qCjmKYz2eU4?t=4027</a><br />\n<br />\n1:07:07<br />\n<br />\n王百羽：<ins><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">民主黨<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黨綱第三條</span></span></strong>：「我們關心中國，<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">作為中国人民的一分子，香港人有權利及責任去參與及評議國家事務。</span></strong>」</ins>如果民主黨孭住「身為中国人」呢個包袱，喺將來中国話唔可以幫助手足嗰陣，<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">喺中国同香港之間，你會揀關心中国定幫助手足</span></strong>？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">涂謹申：</span></span></strong>我唔認為呢個係包袱，作為中國人我地應該係可以評議中共點樣國和做得唔好。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個唔係包袱，呢個係中國人既權利！你話我大中華膠都好！我係中国人！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n王百羽：<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">２０２０年啦，我地見到好多大中華膠既前輩都已經作出心態既改變，但涂謹申仍然未能放棄呢個包袱。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢班人重點，仲係果個已經廢左既立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nＢＴＷ佢地好撚正<br />\n泛民同社民連<br />\n老一輩果班就仲係大中華膠<br />\n但後生果班，點都會有鄺仔，同埋岑子杰，係走另一條路線，呢條路線我係好ａｐｐｒｅｃｉａｔｅ既<br />\n但問題係，同一個黨兩種作風，本身根本無可能發生既<br />\n正常就會好似ＧＡＲＹ　ＦＡＮ咁退黨啦<br />\n所以簡單Ｄ黎講，佢地黨入面既共識係兩邊既票都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好明顯有哂計劃<br />\n呢兩個黨骨子裡會做Ｄ乜<br />\n呢十幾年大家有眼睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}